---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Browse by Category"
description: "Browse all peptide and research compound notes by category. Tissue repair, anti-aging, GLP-1, cognitive research, and more."
ogDescription: "Browse all peptide and research compound notes by category."
---

<nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
  <a href="/">Home</a>
  <span>&rsaquo;</span>
  Browse by Category
</nav>

<header class="article-header">
  <h1>Browse by Category</h1>
  <p class="lede">Each research notes page is tagged by the areas researchers study it for. Select a category to see all related compounds.</p>
</header>

<div class="tag-grid">
  {% for tagGroup in collections.noteTags %}
    <a href="/tags/{{ tagGroup.slug }}/" class="tag-card">
      <span class="tag-card-name">{{ tagGroup.name }}</span>
      <span class="tag-card-desc">{{ tagGroup.description }}</span>
      <span class="tag-card-count">{{ tagGroup.items.length }} {% if tagGroup.items.length == 1 %}compound{% else %}compounds{% endif %}</span>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
